# Assets Deferred Tax Assets From Tax Losses Current Amount

## identifier
de8912

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of  Deferred Tax Assets arising out of tax losses that are current. This item is to be determined in accordance with relevant accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.DeferredTaxAssetsFromTaxLossesCurrent.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.06
- period=instant
